# 📊 Employee Attrition Analysis
---

## 📌 Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing employee attrition data to identify the key factors influencing employee turnover across different departments. The analysis helps in understanding patterns and improving employee retention strategies.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Microsoft Excel  
- Data Cleaning & Analysis  
- Basic Data Visualization  

---

## 📈 Key Insights
- 📉 Attrition rate varies significantly across departments  
- 🏢 Certain departments show higher employee turnover  
- 📊 Patterns identified using data-driven analysis  
- 📌 Insights can help in improving retention strategies  

---


## 🎯 Conclusion
The project highlights important trends in employee attrition and provides actionable insights that can help organizations make better HR decisions and reduce employee turnover.

